<h3>Help - myIATA Self Service Portal</h3>
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="95%" border="0" class="basictable"><thead><tr class="Whsep Wvsep"><td>Company Account - Trusted Companies</td>
</tr>
</thead><tbody><tr><td><h3><strong>Purpose:</strong></h3>
<ul><li>On this screen User can view network of companies affiliated to users current company. User can Give Trust to other companies in the network.</li>
<li>User's current company is highlighted in a different color. Companies registered with IATA are marked with green tick mark <img height="21" alt="registered" width="21" align="absbottom" src="http://localhost:80/PortalDocroot/images/ico_approved.gif"></img></li>
<li>Companies not registered are denoted by the red colored stop icon <img height="21" alt="Not Registered" width="21" align="absmiddle" src="http://localhost:80/PortalDocroot/images/ico_declined.gif"></img></li>
</ul>
<h4><strong>Actions:</strong></h4>
<ul><li>Select the Check box of the company to build trust .</li>
<li>Unselect the check box the company to remove trust.</li>
<li>Companies where <strong>trust is denied</strong> are grayed out.</li>
<li>To <strong>choose all</strong> the companies (which have enabled trust intake) select the check box preceding the header <strong>Trusted</strong></li>
<li>Click on <strong>Save Changes</strong> to update the lists.</li>
<li>Click on <strong>Cancel Changes</strong> to discard all actions.</li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
